========================================
DATABASE
========================================

Use PostgreSQL.

Requirements:
- UUID PK
- Indexes on foreign keys
- Proper constraints
- Soft delete where needed
- Created_at / updated_at
- Migrations

Generate:
- ER diagram (text)
- Full migration files

========================================
REDIS
========================================

Use for:
- Gym load realtime counters
- Session cache
- Rate limiting
- Pub/Sub notifications

